OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fwill soon die out this evening leaving
OL,7,Fa dry and mostly clear night across
OL,8,Fthe region, with lighter winds than of
OL,9,Flate. However, some cloud developing
OL,10,Flater, especially in the west. A frost
OL,11,Fforming in rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FEaster Monday will be dry and
OL,14,Fsettled. There will be some cloud at
OL,15,Ftimes, especially in the west at
OL,16,Ffirst, with a generally sunnier
OL,17,Fafternoon unfolding. Fairly breezy,
OL,18,Fbut mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
