OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday looks dry, bright and breezy
OL,7,Fwith warm hazy sunshine in the east.
OL,8,FCloudier on Wednesday, with overnight
OL,9,Frain introducing a colder day on
OL,10,FThursday with sunshine and blustery
OL,11,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
